                <h4 data-uuid="2a9935d6f72c44dcaea18f89d1e1556a">Main Idea</h4>
                <p class="main-idea" data-uuid="28f456e3edef4b76ab4e549569724df4">The First Amendment guarantees basic freedoms to individuals.</p>
                <h2 data-uuid="3d78256ed358468e80fde75d869c9717">First Amendment</h2>
                <div class="yellow-star-yellow-bar" data-uuid="6368b0e973734fedb41f2fe0505322a5"></div>
            </article>
        </section>
        <section class="graphic-organizer-prompt " data-uuid="44af754263c44deb900b8b7082f038b5">
            <div class="go-prompt-bottom-bar" data-uuid="5ddf3c2afe42431095c86a7a9c783649">
                <p data-uuid="34032f57242a4901bbb2109df33fd42e">As you read, use the graphic organizer to take notes on the First Amendment.</p>
            </div>
