        <h3 data-uuid="c238c1f2030746dd903379759272665a">Freedom of Assembly</h3>
        <p data-uuid="f466bbadcd1043c994c9eaaa53963b25"> Americans also have freedom of assembly, or of holding meetings. Any group may gather to discuss issues or conduct business. If people gather peacefully and do not engage in illegal activities, the government cannot interfere.</p>
