        <h3 data-uuid="459587d7383b44a4b7a83ed48b27b628">Right to Petition</h3>
        <p data-uuid="8d15065b743d4793af148c0778018520">The right to <b><dfn title="petition">petition</dfn></b>, or make a request of the government, is another right of the American people. Any American can present a petition to a government official. This right lets Americans show dissatisfaction with a law. They can also suggest new laws.</p>
